{"tid":2327602,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"史維：科大廣州校園料2022年開學　畢業生可擁港科大學位","createTime":"2020-12-16T07:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T17:49:42.000Z","uid":225931,"like":5,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"10aa8df4187293205161216b573dbf6e29cf4979","tid":2327602,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:31:30.000Z","msg":"接連有本地大學進軍內地及大灣區。香港科技大學位於廣州市南沙區的新校園，工程項目上月獲批展開，校方預料，港科大（廣州）可於2022年9月正式開學，首階段以招收4,000名研究生為目標。<br />\n<br />\n科大校長史維強調，新校園與清水灣校園優勢互補，兩校學科不會重疊。他又強調，雖然兩校非從屬關係，但未來畢業生均同擁科大學位。據了解，兩校學生可親身或以網上方式，選修另一校園課程。即使循廣州校園入學，只需符合科大畢業資格及條件，亦可獲頒科大畢業證書。"},{"pid":"d8e097b6b3c7eab32453718e9cf23836b941297d","tid":2327602,"uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76965ff3ea36f07e43f7549b5058bca06d4664b","tid":2327602,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:32:44.000Z","msg":"等我過返去讀個degree先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf00eeb77fcf2d0e82fd5116071cf9b0ae121c62","tid":2327602,"uid":275477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:33:54.000Z","msg":"等我去買返個博士學位先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94863cb1c0dfa2d2aba3a8f440386e0ca1ac1651","tid":2327602,"uid":8308,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"咁我讀完科大計唔計廣州科大學位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知去大灣區冇返個廣州titile好蝕底"},{"pid":"913a8c94268a31318067bb90ae51a1b0f909b605","tid":2327602,"uid":200328,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"科大生RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你讀完同大陸讀垃圾大學無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6166adb506d06b99f7d6555eb7c06e207f98757c","tid":2327602,"uid":22